snippet.title: Amber Heard opens up about being domestic abuse survivor - #ANI News
snippet.description:
New Delhi, Nov 28 (ANI): Actor Amber Heard talked about being a domestic abuse survivor. E! Online reported that in an interview with an American magazine, Glamour she asked about the aforementioned topic without remarking ex-spouse Johnny Depp’s name.
